    \"stem\": \"You are a junior doctor in a busy emergency department. Two patients arrive simultaneously, both requiring immediate attention. Patient A is a young child with severe respiratory distress. Patient B is an elderly person with chest pain and suspected myocardial infarction. There is only one free bed and one doctor available to assess.\",
