    \"topic\": \"Ethical Dilemma - Best Interest\",
    \"stem\": \"An unconscious patient arrives in the ED with no next of kin. They have a 'Do Not Resuscitate' (DNR) tattoo on their chest, but no formal documentation to support it. The medical team is divided on whether to resuscitate if they arrest.\",
