    \"correct_answer\": 1,
    \"explanation\": \"The most constructive first step is to communicate directly and privately with the team member. There might be underlying issues affecting their participation. This approach offers a chance to resolve the problem collaboratively. Excluding them or immediately reporting them can be counterproductive and unprofessional without a prior attempt at resolution.\",
    \"metadata\": {
      \"difficulty\": \"medium\",
      \"section_type\": \"situational_judgement\"
    }
  },
  {
    \"type\": \"situational_judgement\",
    \"topic\": \"Feedback & Improvement\",
    \"stem\": \"You receive critical feedback on your performance from a senior colleague, which you feel is unfair and demotivating.\",
