    \"explanation\": \"Receiving feedback, even if it feels unfair, is an opportunity for growth. The most professional approach is to listen, seek clarification, and reflect on it. This demonstrates maturity and a commitment to improvement. Becoming defensive or dismissing feedback prevents learning. Complaining to others is unprofessional.\",
