    \"explanation\": \"It's important to recognise your limitations and seek appropriate guidance when undertaking new tasks. This ensures patient safety and your own professional development. Attempting it alone or declining outright are not ideal. Seeking supervision and reviewing protocols is the most responsible approach.\",
