    \"explanation\": \"Supporting new colleagues, especially those from different backgrounds, is crucial for effective teamwork and patient care. Offering private, constructive support and guidance is the most appropriate and empathetic approach. Public correction can be humiliating. Reporting without first offering support is unhelpful.\",
