    \"correct_answer\": 2,
    \"explanation\": \"It's important to be honest but also to ensure that complex and sensitive information is delivered by the most appropriate person (usually the consultant) and in a planned, supportive manner. Acknowledge their question and fear, but defer the full discussion to the consultant, while ensuring it happens promptly. Lying or avoiding the question is unethical.\",
    \"metadata\": {
      \"difficulty\": \"medium\",
      \"section_type\": \"situational_judgement\"
    }
  },
  {
