      \"Help your friend, assuming you can somehow finish your assignment late at night.\",
      \"Assess the urgency and nature of your friend's emergency. If truly critical, offer help for a defined period, then return to your assignment, communicating potential delays to your tutor if necessary. If not critical, politely explain your commitments.\",
