    \"correct_answer\": 2,
    \"explanation\": \"This tests prioritisation and communication skills. You need to balance personal commitments with professional responsibilities. Assessing the emergency's true urgency is key. Offering limited, focused help or explaining your constraints is more responsible than outright refusal or over-committing. Communication is essential.\",
