    \"correct_answer\": 1,
    \"explanation\": \"A thorough handover is crucial for patient safety. You must advocate for a complete handover, explaining its importance. Accepting an incomplete handover puts patients at risk. If the colleague refuses, escalation to a senior is necessary. Complaining to others is unprofessional and unhelpful.\",
    \"metadata\": {
      \"difficulty\": \"medium\",
      \"section_type\": \"situational_judgement\"
    }
  },
  {
