    \"topic\": \"Compassion & Empathy\",
    \"stem\": \"A patient has just received devastating news about their prognosis. They are visibly distraught and crying.\",
    \"passage\": null,
    \"options\": [
      \"Leave the room to give them privacy, assuming they prefer to be alone.\",
      \"Tell them that you understand how they feel and that they need to be strong.\",
      \"Sit with them, offer a comforting presence, listen empathetically if they want to talk, and ask if there's anything you can do to help.\",
